imdb.plot outline: Ascentreks is an American television series that follows the adventures of investigative explorers Wes Hoffman and Jake Washburn, along with their film crew Lyndon Alvarez and Jon Ratzlaff, as they seek out in search of the most eccentric people, places and things that they can find. In each episode, the crew determines the subject of their exploration and brings you the viewer along for the adventures, treks, and investigations.
imdb.title: Ascentreks
plot: _Ascentreks_ (qv) is an American television series that follows the adventures of investigative explorers Wes Hoffman and Jake Washburn, along with their film crew Lyndon Alvarez and Jon Ratzlaff, as they seek out in search of the most eccentric people, places and things that they can find. In each episode, the crew determines the subject of their exploration and brings you the viewer along for the adventures, treks, and investigations.
